    "_postman_id": "6123716f-23ab-45c5-a51b-f42f0c1388f2",
    "name": "Finance Tracker API",
    "description": "# Finance Tracker API\n\n**Base URL:** `{{Assignment}}` → `http://localhost:8000/api/v1`\n\nA comprehensive Financial Dashboard API for managing users, financial records, and analytics. Built with role-based access control (RBAC) and secure HTTP-only cookie authentication.\n\n---\n\n## 🔐 Authentication\n\nThis API uses **HTTP-only cookies** for authentication. Upon a successful login, the server sets two cookies automatically:\n\n| Cookie | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `accessToken` | Short-lived JWT for authenticating requests |\n| `refreshToken` | Long-lived token used to refresh the access token |\n\n> **Note:** You do not need to manually set any `Authorization` headers. Cookies are handled automatically by Postman when \"Automatically follow redirects\" and cookie handling are enabled.\n\n---\n\n## 👥 Roles\n\n| Role | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `viewer` | Default role. Can only see their own financial data. |\n| `analyst` | Can view all company-wide financial records and dashboard stats. |\n| `admin` | Full access. Can create employees, manage all records, and view all stats. |\n\n---\n\n## 📁 Endpoints Overview\n\n| Module | Prefix | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| Authentication | `/auth` | Register, login, profile, logout, employee creation |\n| Financial Records | `/records` | CRUD operations on financial records |\n| Dashboard | `/dashboard` | Summary stats and monthly trends |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Common HTTP Status Codes\n\n| Code | Meaning |\n|---|---|\n| `200` | OK — Request succeeded |\n| `201` | Created — Resource successfully created |\n| `400` | Bad Request — Validation error or missing fields |\n| `401` | Unauthorized — Not logged in or token expired |\n| `403` | Forbidden — Insufficient permissions or account inactive |\n| `404` | Not Found — Resource does not exist |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "37266975",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/37266975-6123716f-23ab-45c5-a51b-f42f0c1388f2?source=collection_link"
  },
