            "description": "## Get All Records\n\nRetrieves financial records. `viewer` role users see only their own records. `analyst` and `admin` roles can see all records across the organization.\n\n**Auth required:** Yes (via `accessToken` cookie)\n\n**Query Parameters (optional):**\n\n| Parameter | Type | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `type` | string | Filter by `income` or `expense` |\n| `category` | string | Filter by category name |\n| `startDate` | string | Filter records from this date (ISO 8601) |\n| `endDate` | string | Filter records up to this date (ISO 8601) |\n\n**Success Response (200):** Returns an array of financial record objects.\n\n**Error Responses:**\n- `401` — Not logged in or token expired"
